---
import Breadcrumbs from '../../components/Breadcrumbs.astro'
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro'
---
<Layout title="Work With Rank4AI – AI Search Visibility Services & Pricing" description="AI search visibility services from Rank4AI. Ecosystem from £800/mo, full agency from £1,500/mo. Starts with an audit across six AI platforms.">

<section class="pt-12 pb-24 reveal">
  <div class="container-narrow">
    <Breadcrumbs items={[
      { label: 'Home', href: '/' },
      { label: 'What We Do' }
    ]} />

    <p class="section-tag">What We Do</p>
    <h1 class="mb-6">Work With Us</h1>

    <img src="/images/content/ai-search-signals.svg" alt="AI search visibility signals" class="w-full rounded-xl mb-8 mt-6" loading="lazy">
    <p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-5">Rank4AI is a UK AI search agency. We get your business recommended by ChatGPT, Claude, Gemini, Perplexity, Copilot and Google AI.</p>
    <p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-5">Every engagement begins with an AI Search Visibility Audit. Before we recommend anything, we test your current visibility across all six major AI platforms, identify the gaps across all five signal layers and tell you exactly what the right starting point is.</p>
    <p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-10">There is no obligation beyond the audit. Some clients use the findings to self-action. Some choose advisory. Some start on a service. The audit tells us what makes sense – you choose the pace.</p>

    <h2 class="mb-4">Two Paths</h2>
    <p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-8">Our services are structured in two ways. The ecosystem service builds presence outside your website entirely. The full agency service includes your website directly. Both begin with the audit.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="container">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-16">
      <a href="/what-we-do/ecosystem-services/" class="card group">
        <h3 class="!text-xl text-teal mb-3">Ecosystem Services – No Site Work</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-4">Everything we build sits outside your existing website. No code changes, no redesigns, no disruption to your current setup.</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-text-muted mb-2">Google Foundation from £800/mo</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-text-muted mb-2">Core Ecosystem from £1,300/mo</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-text-muted mb-4">Full Ecosystem from £2,500/mo</p>
        <span class="link text-sm">Learn more &rarr;</span>
      </a>
      <a href="/what-we-do/full-agency/" class="card group">
        <h3 class="!text-xl text-teal mb-3">Full Agency – Includes Site Work</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-4">We work on your website directly alongside the full ecosystem build. Technical implementation, content restructure, authority architecture.</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-text-muted mb-2">Standard from £1,500/mo</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-text-muted mb-2">Strategic from £3,000/mo</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-text-muted mb-4">Partner from £5,000/mo</p>
        <span class="link text-sm">Learn more &rarr;</span>
      </a>
    </div>

    <div class="container-narrow">
      <h2 class="mb-4">The Five Signal Model</h2>
      <p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-8">AI systems form confidence in a business through five signal layers. Our audit measures all five. Our work strengthens whichever ones need it.</p>

      <div class="space-y-6 mb-16">
        <div class="card-teal-border">
          <h3 class="!text-lg text-teal mb-2">Identity Clarity</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-text-muted leading-relaxed">Can the AI clearly define what your business is? If different sources describe it differently, the system becomes uncertain. Uncertain businesses do not get recommended.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card-teal-border">
          <h3 class="!text-lg text-teal mb-2">Subject Authority</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-text-muted leading-relaxed">Does your business clearly demonstrate expertise in a specific area? AI systems favour specialists. Authority comes from structured expertise, not content volume.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card-teal-border">
          <h3 class="!text-lg text-teal mb-2">Meaning Architecture</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-text-muted leading-relaxed">Is the structure of your website easy for AI systems to read, extract from and summarise? The technical and structural foundations determine whether AI systems can reliably interpret what you do.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card-teal-border">
          <h3 class="!text-lg text-teal mb-2">Ecosystem Validation</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-text-muted leading-relaxed">Do independent sources across the web confirm what your site says? Your website alone is limited evidence. Many consistent independent voices are strong evidence.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card-teal-border">
          <h3 class="!text-lg text-teal mb-2">Signal Consistency</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-text-muted leading-relaxed">Does your business describe itself consistently over time? Stability compounds. Rebrands, category changes and terminology drift reset interpretation.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <h2 class="mb-4">How We Work</h2>
      <p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-5">Rank4AI is not run like a normal agency. There are no juniors, no handoffs, and no layers between you and the people doing the work.</p>
      <p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-5">We do not do work you cannot understand. If something does not make sense, we explain it. If there are areas you do not want to focus on, that is fine. We advise, but this is your business.</p>

      <h2 class="mb-4 mt-16">The Platforms We Cover</h2>
      <p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-8">Our work addresses visibility across all six major AI platforms. Each sources differently. Each requires a different mix of signals.</p>

      <div class="space-y-4 mb-16">
        <div class="card"><h3 class="!text-base text-teal mb-1">ChatGPT &amp; SearchGPT</h3><p class="text-sm text-text-muted">Bing is ChatGPT's primary web retrieval index. Building in the Microsoft and Bing ecosystem is the most direct ChatGPT visibility strategy available.</p></div>
        <div class="card"><h3 class="!text-base text-teal mb-1">Claude</h3><p class="text-sm text-text-muted">Indexed web content and training data. Clear entity definition and multiple independent sources describing the business consistently.</p></div>
        <div class="card"><h3 class="!text-base text-teal mb-1">Gemini</h3><p class="text-sm text-text-muted">Google's AI assistant. Draws from Google's index, Knowledge Graph, and Google-owned infrastructure.</p></div>
        <div class="card"><h3 class="!text-base text-teal mb-1">Perplexity</h3><p class="text-sm text-text-muted">Real-time open web crawler. Explicitly cites sources. High-trust, well-structured, indexed content performs well.</p></div>
        <div class="card"><h3 class="!text-base text-teal mb-1">Copilot</h3><p class="text-sm text-text-muted">Microsoft's AI assistant. Bing index plus a direct data relationship with LinkedIn via Microsoft ownership.</p></div>
        <div class="card"><h3 class="!text-base text-teal mb-1">Google AI Overviews</h3><p class="text-sm text-text-muted">Pulls from Google's own index and Google-owned platforms. The most direct route is the Google ecosystem.</p></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>


    <!-- Internal links -->
    <div class="mt-12 pt-8 border-t border-border">
      <h2 class="!text-xl mb-4">Related</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-3">
                <a href="/what-we-do/ai-visibility-audit/" class="card group text-sm"><span class="font-medium text-teal group-hover:text-accent">AI Visibility Audit</span></a>
        <a href="/about/five-signal-framework/" class="card group text-sm"><span class="font-medium text-teal group-hover:text-accent">The Five Signal Model</span></a>
        <a href="/free-audit/" class="card group text-sm"><span class="font-medium text-accent">Get a Free Audit &rarr;</span></a>

      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="bg-off-white border-t border-border text-center py-24 px-10">
    <h2 class="mb-4">Get Started</h2>
    <p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted mb-10 max-w-[500px] mx-auto">Every engagement begins with the AI Search Visibility Audit. We test your current visibility across all six platforms and tell you exactly where to start.</p>
    <a href="/free-audit/" class="cta-primary">Get a Free AI Search Visibility Audit &rarr;</a>
    <p class="mt-4"><a href="/book-a-call/" class="link text-sm">Or book a call &rarr;</a></p>
  </div>
</section>

</Layout>
